OL,3,CUK pharmacy sector 'the sick man of
OL,4,CEurope'
OL,6,FThe UK is the "sick man of Europe"
OL,7,Fwhen it comes to spending on medicines
OL,8,Fand community pharmacies, leaders from
OL,9,Fthe sector have said.
OL,11,FThe National Pharmacy Association
OL,12,F(NPA) urged the Government to "get
OL,13,Fround the table and start to deliver
OL,14,Fthe funding necessary" to stop
OL,15,Fpharmacies closing and improve care
OL,16,Ffor patients.
