OL,3,CUK pharmacy sector 'the sick man of
OL,4,CEurope'
OL,6,FNPA analysis of Organisation for
OL,7,FEconomic Co-operation and Development
OL,8,F(OECD) figures found the UK has fewer
OL,9,Fpharmacies per 100,000 people than the
OL,10,Flikes of Ireland, France, Spain,
OL,11,FPortugal, Latvia, Romania and Bulgaria.
OL,13,FIt said the average UK pharmacy also
OL,14,Fserves more customers ` about 5,700 `
OL,15,Fthan those in France (3,238) and
OL,16,FIreland (2,500).
