OL,3,CUK pharmacy sector 'the sick man of
OL,4,CEurope'
OL,6,FThe analysis found the UK also spends
OL,7,Fless on medicines per head of
OL,8,Fpopulation than Ireland, Australia,
OL,9,FJapan, the US, Spain, Germany and
OL,10,FItaly.
OL,12,FGermany spends double what the UK
OL,13,Fdoes, according to the NPA.
OL,15,FNPA chairman Nick Kaye said: "These
OL,16,Fshocking new figures show that the UK
OL,17,Fis the 'sick man of Europe' when it
OL,18,Fcomes to spending on vital medicines
OL,19,Fand community pharmacies.
OL,26,@wD@^OU
