OL,3,CUK pharmacy sector 'the sick man of
OL,4,CEurope'
OL,6,F"It is damning that UK pharmacies
OL,7,Fserve more patients than comparative
OL,8,Fcountries whilst also receiving ever
OL,9,Freducing levels of funding."
OL,11,FThe analysis comes after members of
OL,12,Fthe NPA voted in favour of collective
OL,13,Faction in a row over funding.
OL,15,FThe trade association said this could
OL,16,Fmean fewer pharmacies will be open in
OL,17,Fevenings or at weekends, with some
OL,18,Fpotentially withdrawing from locally
OL,19,Fcommissioned services such as
OL,20,Femergency contraception, addiction
OL,21,Fsupport and stop smoking services.
