OL,6,FMr Kaye added: "As our ballot result
OL,7,Fshowed, many pharmacy owners feel
OL,8,Fpushed to breaking point thanks to the
OL,9,Fimpact of 40% cuts to their funding
OL,10,Fand increases in their workload.
OL,12,F"Community pharmacies have the
OL,13,Fpotential to deliver so much more for
OL,14,Fpatients, including a wider range of
OL,15,Fclinical services that will help to
OL,16,Fkeep pressure off other parts of our
OL,17,Fhealth system.
OL,19,F"However, this cannot happen with
OL,20,Ffunding at its current levels and
OL,21,Fpharmacies shutting at record rates.
OL,26,@nD@POUtD@AOU{D@AOU
