OL,6,F"The Government must get round the
OL,7,Ftable and start to deliver the funding
OL,8,Fnecessary so we can stop the closures
OL,9,Fand deliver the best possible care for
OL,10,Fpatients."
OL,12,FThe Department of Health and Social
OL,13,FCare has been approached for comment.
